    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hyalella cuyana n. sp., male holotype (FML-CRUST 01282). A left maxilliped B labrum C lower lip D left mandible E right mandible F internal lateral view of maxilla 1 G maxilla 1 H maxilla 2. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
