    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Hyalella cuyana n. sp., male holotype (FML-CRUST 01282). A pleopod 3 B uropod 1 C uropod 2 D uropod 3 E telson of male paratype F telson lateral view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
